But..anyone notice the epic quest item yet for us? Here are the stats..anything I posted before was wrong, sorry..<p>

Celestial fists- type armor gloves<p>

AC 15<br>
+100 hp<br>
+20 str<br>
+10 sta (adds another 40 hp for 140 total), agi (nice bit of AC added), dex<br>
+10 all saves<br>
perm effect: Celestial Tranquility: 40% haste, does NOT stack with FBSS/CoF/haste armor, but does stack with ROTWF, ench, bard, and shaman spells, also +40 str (making it +60 total)<p>

Gloves, not a weapon. Also, the particle effect (a couple of floating yin-yangs) does NOT show up when a weapon is wielded..this leads me to believe that they may be thinking about improving our fists..I hope so I'd prefer them myself...</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
