<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Told the ROTWF mobs aren't NEARLY as bad as Raster is in terms of spawn rates..oh and there is an alternative to camping these guys once you get high enough for the fists (min 46 recommended 50+)<p>

Get yourself 2-3 decent groups around 50 or so in level<p>

Make sure you bring some clerics<p>

Head to Rathe mtns and hunt down Zethyl. Give him 2 shovels or torches or whatever so he can't dual wield<p>

beat the stuffing out of him<p>

loot the ROTLC :)<p>

Most of the high-levels I know are probably going to take this much faster option..after all by 50 you probably know an army of people who'd be bored enough to help you with this :)<p>

BTW, fists are getting changed AGAIN, due to MASSIVE monk complaints (led by Wakefieldsucks, the monk on Test server that first got the gloves). Patch will be in this Tuesday, and Kaiaren, the mob the quest is based around, will be put back in game (He was removed because someone figured out how to get mad xp from him free)</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
